<p></p>
<a href="/recipes/food/views/Tropical-Carrot-Cake-with-Coconut-Cream-Cheese-Frosting-107949"><h3>Tropical Carrot Cake with Coconut Cream Cheese Frosting</h3></a>

<br /><br />
<p><span class="dropCapFirst">A</span>
 twist on the usual carrot cake, this one features coconut, macadamia nuts, and pineapple. For added oomph, cream of coconut is beaten into the frosting.</p> 

