                                            <a class="rcm_title" href="/articlesguides/cuisines/aroundtheworldin80dishes/austriasachertorterecipe">Austrian Sachertorte Recipe and Video</a>

                                            
                                            <span class="rcm_article_archive_dek">Visit Vienna, Austria, with Around the World in 80 Dishes and learn to make this famous confection&#151;a dense chocolate cake with apricot jam, chocolate glaze, and whipped cream </span>
                                        </p>
                                   </div>
